data.description: Very rare 5 bdrm 2 bth ranch. Huge master with nice walkin closet. Lots of changes since 2015 Real hardwood floors. Very open floor plan now. Kitchen/living room over 600 sqft. Lots of cabinets & countertop with room to expand more. This home sits on a nice corner lot with 2 driveways. Has a 3 car garage with one bay that has an oil pit. Also 1 tall door.Lots of parking. Has Conex that could be available. New boiler & HVAC in 2020. Had Quiter Home Program done prior to this sale. All windows and doors and HVAC system installed in 2007. New roof 2012. Definitely worth a look. So much to see!!!  With acceptable offer Seller will consider painting living room and kitchen.
